CBRE are pleased to offer to market for lease 45 Dickson Avenue, Artarmon.

The property is ideally located on the corner of Dickson Ave and Clarendon Street giving exceptional exposure to this intersection.

The whole building offers 850sqm of modern office accommodation and unrivalled showroom which has direct street access from Dickson Ave. The property is perfect as a corporate HQ, retail showroom or hi-tech warehouse.

For more information or to arrange an inspection, please contact Peter Mangraviti on 0413 750 350 or Geoff Hunt on 0439 963 623

CBRE are pleased to present Unit 9/76 Reserve Road to market for lease.

The property is ideally located in a well-presented modern industrial estate at the southern end of Reserve Road. 

It also enjoys an unrivalled location close to the Royal North Shore Hospital, Bunnings and Home HQ.

The property offers a 168.6sqm unit with attractive ratio of office to warehouse with access via a 4m height roller door.

There are 2 car spaces included with the property.

For more information or to arrange an inspection, please contact the exclusive CBRE agent Peter Mangraviti on 0413 750 350

Well located on Reserve Road close to the recently refurbished Home Maker Centre and next to the Royal North Shore Hospital. This property offers easy access to the M2 motorway, North Sydney CBD and Sydney CBD.

For more information or to arrange an inspection, please contact exclusive leasing agents

CBRE are pleased to offer for sale and lease via expression of interest 18-26 Dickson Avenue, Artarmon.

A rare opportunity to acquire a modern and functional freestanding industrial facility located in the North Shores most sought after suburb.

Key features Include:
- Well presented freestanding industrial building with true street presence and exposure.
- Modern and attractive office accommodation split over two levels.
- Functional high clearance, clear span warehouse with sunken loading dock.
- Flexible IN1 General Industrial zoning which allows for a multitude of uses (STCA).
- 8 min drive to the Sydney CBD and 4 min to North Sydney CBD.
- Close proximity to an enviable amount of amenities including bus transport, northern rail network, Bunnings and the Home Maker Centre.

CBRE strongly recommend your consideration of this outstanding asset.

For further information or to arrange an inspection please contact the exclusive agents.

Peter Mangraviti 0413 750 350
Matthew Lee 0404 838 325

Situated in the heart of the Artarmon, this property enjoys easy access to all parts of Sydney. Epping Road takes you west to the M2 Motorway and east to the CBD's of Chatswood, North Sydney and Sydney.

This building features dual street access which allows for the property to be divided in to two separate tenancies and is suitable for a wide range of industrial/commercial uses.

An ideal corporate HQ with excellent street presence and modern facade. 

Building area: 780sqm*
Cap spaces: 9 secure basement spaces

For more information or to arrange an inspection, please call exclusive CBRE agents Peter Mangraviti or Geoff Hunt
